and maintain "productivity and efficiency in today's
competitive legal market". A printed study guide
accompanies each tape. The titles include "From Law School
to Law Practice: What Every Associate Needs to Know" (two
parts), "Law Firm Marketing and Professional
Responsibility", "Avoiding or Surviving Law Firm
Break-Ups", and "Law Firm Policies on Sexual Harassment:
Development and Implementation". Each tape costs $75.





